Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:14.16,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\pos(318,396)\c&HA6D1DB&\iclip(297.14,387.81,1005.71,446.48)\t(0,2315,\iclip(1005.71,387.81,1006.47,447.24))}我…名…是柏…拉…8。我…是、残…次…
